## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

The **University Admissions Bot** helps prospective students navigate the college admission process efficiently. Instead of searching through lengthy university websites, users can ask questions and receive instant, accurate responses.

This project focuses on compressing admission-related information into an easy-to-use conversational interface.

